annoGroup.heading: Editor's Notes
annoGroup.text: This subchapter expired on January 1, 2011, pursuant to section 3 of D.C. Law 18-35.
Section 3 of D.C. Law 18-35 provided: “Section 2(b) enacting this subchapter shall expire on January 1, 2011.”
